    <abstract>
      <title>Abstract</title>
      <sec id="s1">
        <title>Summary</title>
        <p>MetExploreViz is an open source web component that can be easily embedded in any web site. It provides features dedicated to the visualization of metabolic networks and pathways and thus offers a flexible solution to analyse omics data in a biochemical context.</p>
      </sec>
      <sec id="s2">
        <title>Availability and implementation</title>
        <p>Documentation and link to GIT code repository (GPL 3.0 license) are available at this URL: <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://metexplore.toulouse.inra.fr/metexploreViz/doc/">http://metexplore.toulouse.inra.fr/metexploreViz/doc/</ext-link></p>
      </sec>
